channel.title: Great things to do while high
channel.description:
Whats something you have done while high that 'blew your mind'.
Watched wizard of oz played at same time as dark side of the moon.
alot of parts line up and its seriously a trip.
You can watch em on youtube... this guy uploaded the whole hting in parts... here they are: http://www.youtube.com/profile_videos?user=meowcat89&p=r

item.title: Great things to do while high
item.dc:creator: @ThatOneServer Mike_
item.description:

[quote=“jme, post:2, topic:209159”][quote author=ThatOneServer link=topic=275547.msg2249529#msg2249529 date=1212134756]
Whats something you have done while high that ‘blew your mind’.

Watched wizard of oz played at same time as dark side of the moon.

alot of parts line up and its seriously a trip.

You can watch em on youtube… this guy uploaded the whole hting in parts… here they are:
http://www.youtube.com/profile_videos?user=meowcat89&p=r
[/quote]

Haha I love doing that. Playing a song and watching TV commericials or something. Trips the hell out of you especially with friends. I remember playing “a white christmas” and its basically some christmas jingle made up of different cats going ‘meow’ and it was the funniest thing ever.[/quote]
do the oz one… its a pretty well known trick…
